<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA624_05_IH_0003</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema624_05.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema624_05_ih_0003">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="3_deep_green" lang="y">비례식의 성질을 이용하여 비례식을 모두 찾아 ○표 하세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center">
          <div class="text_area">
            <ul>
              <li>9:2=54:12</li>
              <li>0.7:1.3=14:26</li>
              <li class="flex align_center">
                <span class="fraction_box"> <span>1</span><span>6</span> </span>
                :
                <span class="fraction_box"> <span>2</span><span>3</span> </span>
                =3:2
              </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="boolean_wrap">
              <button data-answer-single="true" class="button1"></button>
              <button data-answer-single="true" class="button2"></button>
              <button data-answer-single="false" class="button 3"></button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 해설 -->
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p>㉠ 0.8 : 2.7의 전항과 후항에 10을 곱하면 8 : 27이 됩니다.</p>
              
                <p class="mixed_fraction mt_15">
                  ㉡ 후항
                  <span>1</span>
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span>1</span>
                    <span>6</span>
                  </span>
                  을
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span>6</span>
                    <span>7</span>
                  </span>
                  로 바꾼 후
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span>5</span>
                    <span>12</span>
                  </span>
                  <span>:</span>
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span>7</span>
                    <span>6</span>
                  </span>
                  의 전항과 후항에 12를 곱하면 5 : 14가 됩니다.
                </p>
              
                <p class="mixed_fraction mt_15">
                  ㉢ <span>3</span><span>:</span>
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span>2</span>
                    <span>5</span>
                  </span>
                  의 전항과 후항에 5를 곱하면 15 : 2가 됩니다.
                </p>
              
                <p class="mt_15">따라서 간단한 자연수의 비로 옳게 나타낸 것은 ㉢입니다.</p>
              </div>
              
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <!-- <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button> -->
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
